This respository contents the instances used in the work entitiled "Optimization of waste collection through the sequencing of micro-routes and transfer station convenience analysis: an Argentinian case study" submittied to Waste Management & Research. As explained in the referenced manuscript, theese instances correspond to forty-eight instances of the cmbination of three cases (i.e., Current Situation -CS-, Transfer Station Option 1 -TS1-, and Transfer Station Option 2 -TS2-), two shifts (i.e., day and night shift -D/N-), and eight amount of waste levels (i.e., 50%/60%/70%/80%/90%/100%/105%/110%).
